				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>On this week&#8217;s Corona Geek podcast, Noah Malewicz from <a href=http://www.chunkyapps.com/games-apps target="_blank">Chunky Apps</a> and <a href=http://mobileoctopus.com/ target="_blank">Mobile Octopus</a>, showed the panel how to add visual depth and interest to character animations while reducing the number of sprite sheets needed, using Spine and meshes.</p>
