		<title>Corona Geek #185 &#8211; Spine workflow basics and using Tiled as a level editor</title>
		<link>/blog/coronageek/corona-geek-185-spine-workflow-and-using-tiled-as-a-level-editor/</link>
		<comments>/blog/coronageek/corona-geek-185-spine-workflow-and-using-tiled-as-a-level-editor/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 04 May 2016 23:46:35 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Charles McKeever]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Corona Geek]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Google+ Hangouts]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[game development]]></category>
